**purpose:** Nauion Runtime trien[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] khai siraSign Relational Spectral Boundary Protocol qua 11 lop[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME]. KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] hash, KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] HMAC, KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] token. La[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] giao thuc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] niem[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] khoanh[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] khac[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] cai[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] hinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] trong field.

