==WHAT_SIRASIGN_IS_NOT==
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] hash don[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] (SHA-256 pheng[C3:RN_ANG_ENG])
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] HMAC don[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] token Bearer
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] JWT
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] public key signature don[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] route permission don[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
  - khong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] vi[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] lanh[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME], blockchain, web3 ownership
==END==

==WHAT_SIRASIGN_IS==
  "siraSign giu[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] khoanh[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] khac[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] cai[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] hinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] trong field."
  "siraSign cho sinh the[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] so[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] kha[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] neng[C0:RN_ANG_ENG] duoc[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhen[C5:RN_AN_EN] lai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] dung[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nghia[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] sau khi da[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] hien[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] hinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME]."
  
  siraSign = seal(state + spectral_state + field_condition + relation + meaning + causation + authority + audit_lineage)
  
  KHONG[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] PHAI[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]: siraSign = seal(data)
==END==

